</title>
<subSubSection id="EA54F6D8F8947048EC9044AE793099A6" pageId="null" pageNumber="781" type="description">
<paragraph id="649D00647A0A5F15DD01170263F37E90" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="C410544D2423049D8BE163D5D3958D60" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Silene" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="781" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nutans">
<emphasis id="2E16937299DD44DB59D059B5F2AF2BC3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">S. nutans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 11) durch folgende Merkmale (vgl. auch Becherer 1963): 
<emphasis id="E2D470699DA280EFFFE4383F6D5C0A67" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
Sterile Triebe lang und 
<normalizedToken id="F71DA955ABFECFF768E7C2E0B748ACCF" originalValue="dünn" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">duenn</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="17D8D4EFFCEBB20CE56F20236012715D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">die meisten Internodien 3-20mal so lang wie dick</emphasis>
); 40-80 cm hoch; 
<normalizedToken id="837DC328E186F98DC8264A1ECD6426E5" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Blueten</normalizedToken>
in lockeren, 
<emphasis id="91A81BF3B1093B3616BE82C4834ED54D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
oft allseitswendigen 
<normalizedToken id="73CBD92D1D60F1AA436F1503DCC4BF22" originalValue="Blütenständen" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Bluetenstaenden</normalizedToken>
, meist aufrecht oder waagrecht abstehend; 
<normalizedToken id="558F32BCD4BCA56CD1F80A16B761CA21" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
oberseits 
<normalizedToken id="A669963DCAF1D670626F606E1EB66D0A" originalValue="gelblichweiβ" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">gelblichweiβ</normalizedToken>
, unterseits 
<normalizedToken id="216F4E02628918BDDB76BFFF74D4F95D" originalValue="olivgrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">olivgruen</normalizedToken>
bis schmutzigrot;
</emphasis>
Kapsel 8-15 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="1B798D17F2D5D1CA54939DFDEEDE97BC" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="BB12B098D5664896F0B440377DBE9619" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="00CAA89B3AB6469D103A16A5645CB6F4" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F1ECA56D82F35C2120F96FDBCDED0943" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
<emphasis id="CAB057E4BD2AF686DA16A370B03870D0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 24:</emphasis>
Ohne Herkunftsangabe des Materials (D. 
<normalizedToken id="D8544E023C49DB9BE0B46B9426E36F24" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1942).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7ED93744E6B34917A9C44D583E2DED51" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
<emphasis id="F92F26340261EBB4EC8C9D6CD4A4BF27" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Trockene, lockere, kalkreiche 
<normalizedToken id="9614372EC4C91D952094E550D4BF58AA" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Lichte 
<normalizedToken id="8F0B5E74DB085FF551252B448860B6E4" originalValue="Wälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Waelder</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="1A0581F57400D0420788E56A31B2CD4D" originalValue="Gebüsche" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Gebuesche</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="01BB6D62136F6D262C9A2EED65E8E177" originalValue="Waldränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Waldraender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E3D7A17E9A385C2389862C23DFC31EBD" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
<emphasis id="2F5779C57D4804BAFEA368EAA0F9540E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">
<pageBreakToken id="20D9A5CA19ECC2509EC262D342C73E25" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Verbreitung</pageBreakToken>
. Nicht genau bekannt; 
<normalizedToken id="45B87DF2737A223E9C7E5ECA4764F8C3" originalValue="Südalpenpflanze" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">Suedalpenpflanze</normalizedToken>
?.
</emphasis>
- Im Gebiet: Unteres Valsesia, 
<normalizedToken id="82194D6C6B8F1FC55E522044171131B4" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, Comerseeund Langenseegebiet, Veltlin (z. B. Marsara), Bergamasker Alpen (z. B. 
<taxonomicName id="316B458BB36893CF1D7D163714FB80BC" authority="Presolana" authorityName="Presolana" genus="Val" pageId="null" pageNumber="781" rank="species" species="brembana">Val Brembana, Presolana</taxonomicName>
), Vintschgau (Meran); nicht 
<normalizedToken id="BBE870DE49FA1AB72B011863E132D7B8" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="781">haeufig</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
